+```sql
+mysql> COUNT SHARDING RULE;
++--------------------------+----------+-------+
+| rule_name                | database | count |
++--------------------------+----------+-------+
+| sharding_table           | test1    | 2     |
+| sharding_table_reference | test1    | 2     |
+| broadcast_table          | test1    | 0     |
++--------------------------+----------+-------+
+3 rows in set (0.00 sec)
+```
+
+### Reserved word
+
+`COUNT`, `SHARDING`, `RULE`, `FROM`
+
